   "source": [
    "# Deep Site // Whisper Node\n",
    "> **GPU-accelerated speech transcription using OpenAI Whisper**\n",
    "\n",
    "[![Open In Colab](https://colab.research.google.com/assets/colab-badge.svg)](https://colab.research.google.com/github/morongosteve/llama_index/blob/claude/speech-recognition-ui-Ad1Qj/whisper_node_colab.ipynb)\n",
    "\n",
    "**Features:**\n",
    "- Transcribe audio files (mp3, wav, m4a, ogg, flac, webm)\n",
    "- Record directly from your microphone in-browser\n",
    "- Multilingual transcription + auto language detection\n",
    "- Multiple model sizes: `tiny` → `large-v3`\n",
    "- Export transcript as `.txt` or `.srt` subtitles\n",
    "- Gradio UI for easy interaction\n",
    "\n",
    "---\n",
    "**Runtime:** Set to `T4 GPU` for best performance → *Runtime > Change runtime type > T4 GPU*"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Install Dependencies"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "%%capture\n",
